[I] Obvious Unified Compression Helper

[T] Ouch is a CLI tool for compressing and decompressing for various formats.
[T] Currently supporting: .tar, .zip, 7z, .gz, .xz, .lzma, .bz/bz2/bz3, lz4,
[T] .sz, .zst, .rar, .br.

[U] https://github.com/ouch-org/ouch

